name: Earrings & Pendant Set - Evening Star
description: I was originally three 1950 Silverware Oval Dessert Spoons made in America by Oneida. My beautifully detailed silverplate pattern is called Evening Star and is stunning crafted front and back. Each earring piece weighs 4g and is 3cm long. The Pendant is 6g and 10cm long hanging from a delicate sterling silver snake chain. I was recently discovered by Vintage Goddess and lovingly reincarnated into this elegant earring and pendant set – one of only two created.

name: Earrings - Scandinavia
description: I was originally two 1970 Silverware Salad Forks made in America by Oneida. My unique silverplate pattern is called Scandinavia. Each of my pieces weighs 8g and is 6cm long. I was recently discovered by Vintage Goddess and lovingly reincarnated into these one of only four pairs of earrings.

name: Earring & Pendant Set - Magnolia
description: I was originally 1951 Silverware pierced bladed Pie Server and two Teaspoons made in America by Rogers & Bros. My silverplate pattern is called Magnolia and is beautifully crafted on my front and back. My pendant weighs 18g and is 8cm long. My earrings weigh 9g each are 7.5cm long. I was recently discovered by Vintage Goddess and lovingly reincarnated into this one of a kind pendant on a delicate 76cm sterling silver “O” chain with matching earrings.

name: Earrings - Classic Filigree
description: I was originally two 1937 Silverware Salad Forks made in America by William S. Warren of Harmony House. My silverplate pattern is Classic Filigree and is highly detailed on my front and back with an unusual cut out design. I weigh 9g and am 6.5cm long. I was recently discovered by Vintage Goddess and lovingly reincarnated into this gorgeous one of a kind pair of earrings.

name: Earrings - Cotillion
description: I was originally two 1937 Silverware Teaspoons made in America by W.M. Rogers. My silverplate pattern is called Cotillion and is beautifully detailed on my front and back. Each of my pieces weighs 10g and is 6.5cm long. I was recently discovered by Vintage Goddess and lovingly reincarnated into these one of two only earrings.
